throws\n\n@enduml', 'sequence_diagram': '@startuml\n!theme plain\nskinparam participantpadding 20\nskinparam boxpadding 10\n\nbox "Actors" 
#LightBlue\n  actor "ClinicalStaff" as CS\n  actor "BloodBankManagement" as BBM\n  actor "ITTeam" as IT\n  actor "Scheduler" as SCH\nend 
box\n\nbox "Controller" #LightGreen\n  participant "ReservationAPI" as API\nend box\n\nbox "Application" #LightYellow\n  participant 
"ReservationService" as SVC\nend box\n\nbox "Domain" #LightCoral\n  participant "BloodUnit" as BU\n  participant "Reservation" as RES\n  
participant "BloodTypeCompatibilityAlgorithm" as ALGO\nend box\n\nbox "Infrastructure" #LightGray\n  participant "BloodInventoryDatabase" as 
DB\n  participant "ReservationReleaseScheduler" as RRS\n  participant "AdminDashboard" as DASH\nend box\n\n== Reserve Blood Unit ==\n\nCS -> API
: POST /reservations (transfusionRequestId)\nactivate API\n\nAPI -> SVC : initiateReservation(transfusionRequestId)\nactivate SVC\n\nSVC -> SVC 
: authenticate(CS, "Write")\nnote right: JWT token validation\n\nalt Authentication fails\n  SVC --> API : error 401 Unauthorized\n  API --> CS 
: HTTP 401 Unauthorized\n  deactivate SVC\n  deactivate API\nelse Authorized\n  SVC -> ALGO : isCompatible(patientBloodType, 
candidateBloodType)\n  activate ALGO\n  ALGO --> SVC : boolean\n  deactivate ALGO\n\n  alt Incompatible\n    SVC --> API : error 400 Bad Request
(incompatible blood type)\n    API --> CS : HTTP 400 Bad Request\n    deactivate SVC\n    deactivate API\n  else Compatible\n    SVC -> DB : 
findAvailableUnit(compatibleBloodTypes) [SQL]\n    activate DB\n    DB --> SVC : BloodUnit or null\n    deactivate DB\n\n    alt No available 
unit\n      SVC --> API : error 404 Not Found (no compatible units)\n      API --> CS : HTTP 404 Not Found\n      deactivate SVC\n      
deactivate API\n    else Unit found\n      SVC -> BU : reserve()\n      activate BU\n      note over BU : state: available -> reserved\n      BU
--> SVC : success\n      deactivate BU\n\n      SVC -> DB : createReservation(bloodUnitId, transfusionRequestId, timestamp) [SQL]\n      
activate DB\n      DB --> SVC : reservationId\n      deactivate DB\n\n      SVC -> RES : new Reservation(...)\n      activate RES\n      note 
over RES : state: active, expiry = now + 24h\n      RES --> SVC : reservationId\n      deactivate RES\n\n      SVC --> API : reservationId\n    
API --> CS : HTTP 201 Created (reservationId)\n      deactivate SVC\n      deactivate API\n    end\n  end\nend\n\n== Automatic Release After 24h
==\n\nSCH -> RRS : triggerRelease()\nactivate RRS\n\nRRS -> DB : findExpiredReservations() [SQL]\nactivate DB\nDB --> RRS : list of Reservation 
(active, expiry <= now)\ndeactivate DB\n\nloop for each expired reservation\n  RRS -> RES : release()\n  activate RES\n  note over RES : state: 
active -> released\n  RES --> RRS : success\n  deactivate RES\n\n  RRS -> BU : makeAvailable()\n  activate BU\n  note over BU : state: reserved 
-> available\n  BU --> RRS : success\n  deactivate BU\n\n  RRS -> DB : updateReservationStatus(reservationId, "released") [SQL]\n  activate DB\n
DB --> RRS : ok\n  deactivate DB\n\n  RRS -> DB : updateBloodUnitStatus(bloodUnitId, "available") [SQL]\n  activate DB\n  DB --> RRS : ok\n  
deactivate DB\n\n  RRS -> DASH : logReleaseEvent(reservationId)\n  activate DASH\n  DASH --> RRS : logged\n  deactivate DASH\nend\n\nRRS --> SCH
: release completed\ndeactivate RRS\n\n== Issue Transfusion (within 24h) ==\n\nCS -> API : PUT /reservations/{id}/issue\nactivate API\n\nAPI -> 
SVC : issueReservation(reservationId)\nactivate SVC\n\nSVC -> SVC : authenticate(CS, "Write")\nalt Authentication fails\n  SVC --> API : error 
401\n  API --> CS : HTTP 401\n  deactivate SVC\n  deactivate API\nelse Authorized\n  SVC -> DB : getReservation(reservationId) [SQL]\n  activate
DB\n  DB --> SVC : Reservation (with status)\n  deactivate DB\n\n  alt Reservation status != "active"\n    SVC --> API : error 400 Bad Request 
(reservation not active)\n    API --> CS : HTTP 400 Bad Request\n    deactivate SVC\n    deactivate API\n  else Reservation active\n    SVC -> 
RES : isExpired()\n    activate RES\n    RES --> SVC : boolean\n    deactivate RES\n\n    alt Expired\n      SVC --> API : error 409 Conflict 
(reservation expired, already released)\n      API --> CS : HTTP 409 Conflict\n      deactivate SVC\n      deactivate API\n    else Not 
expired\n      SVC -> RES : issue()\n      activate RES\n      note over RES : state: active -> issued\n      RES --> SVC : success\n      
deactivate RES\n\n      SVC -> BU : issue()\n      activate BU\n      note over BU : state: reserved -> issued\n      BU --> SVC : success\n    
deactivate BU\n\n      SVC -> DB : updateReservationStatus(reservationId, "issued") [SQL]\n      activate DB\n      DB --> SVC : ok\n      
deactivate DB\n\n      SVC -> DB : updateBloodUnitStatus(bloodUnitId, "issued") [SQL]\n      activate DB\n      DB --> SVC : ok\n      
deactivate DB\n\n      SVC --> API : success\n      API --> CS : HTTP 200 OK\n      deactivate SVC\n      deactivate API\n    end\n  
