right: No permissions, access denied\nend\n\n== Dashboard Load Flow ==\n\nBBM -> DV : requestDashboardLoad()\n\nalt Both APIs available\n    DV 
-> IA : getStockLevels(aboRhType: ABORhType) : List<StockLevel>\n    note right: [HTTPS] [encrypted at rest]\n    IA --> DV : return 
stockLevels\n    \n    DV -> IA : getExpiringUnits(dateThreshold: Date) : List<ExpiringUnit>\n    note right: [HTTPS] [encrypted at rest]\n    
IA --> DV : return expiringUnits\n    \n    DV -> TRA : getOpenRequests() : List<TransfusionRequest>\n    note right: [HTTPS] [encrypted at 
rest]\n    TRA --> DV : return openRequests\n    \n    DV -> DV : aggregateData(stockLevels, expiringUnits, openRequests)\n    DV -> DV : 
renderDashboard()\n    note right: Post1: Dashboard accessible, Post2: Data up-to-date\n    \nelse Inventory API unavailable\n    DV -> IA : 
getStockLevels()\n    IA --> DV : return 503 Service Unavailable\n    DV -> DV : displayError("Inventory API unavailable")\n    DV -> DV : 
showCachedData()\n    note right: Pre1: Inventory data may be cached\n    \nelse Transfusion Request API unavailable\n    DV -> TRA : 
