getStockLevels()\n    IA --> DV : return 503\n    DV -> TRA : getOpenRequests()\n    TRA --> DV : return 503\n    DV -> DV : 
displayError("Unable to load dashboard data")\n    DV -> DV : showCachedData()\nend\n\n== Dashboard Refresh Flow (Every 60 seconds) ==\n\nalt No
