rest]\n    IA --> DV : return updatedStockLevels\n    \n    DV -> IA : getExpiringUnits(dateThreshold: Date) : List<ExpiringUnit>\n    note 
right: [HTTPS] [encrypted at rest]\n    IA --> DV : return updatedExpiringUnits\n    \n    DV -> TRA : getOpenRequests() : 
List<TransfusionRequest>\n    note right: [HTTPS] [encrypted at rest]\n    TRA --> DV : return updatedOpenRequests\n    \n    DV -> DV : 
updateDashboardDisplay()\n    note right: Post2: Dashboard updated in real time\n    \nelse Previous refresh still in progress\n    DV -> DV : 
