passed\nWhen the system checks inventory\nThen the unit is marked as expired and is no longer available for use\n```", 33: 
'**As a** blood bank staff member\n**I need** to accept transfusion requests specifying required blood type, Rh factor, and 
quantity, and validate request parameters and store them for matching against available inventory\n**So that** requests can 
be accurately processed and matched with available blood supply\n\n### Details and Assumptions\n* The system will accept 
