- DashboardPage.tsx - Stock levels per ABO/Rh type, low stock alerts (<5 units), open transfusion requests, expiring-soon 
badges
- BloodUnitsPage.tsx - List all units with status badges, add new unit form, delete functionality, expiry countdown
- TransfusionRequestsPage.tsx - List all requests, submit new request form with validation result display
- ReservationsPage.tsx - List all reservations, create new reservation (selecting available blood units and requests), 
release functionality
- Layout.tsx - Sticky frosted-glass nav with links to all pages

**API Endpoints Covered (14 calls in services.ts):**
- GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /blood_units
- GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /reservations
- GET/POST /transfusion_requests, GET /transfusion_requests/{request_id}, POST /transfusion_requests/validate

**TypeScript Types (11 interfaces in types/index.ts):**
- BloodUnit, BloodUnitCreate, BloodUnitUpdate
- TransfusionRequestDTO, ValidationResult, StorageResult, SubmitResponse
- Reservation, ReservationCreate, ReservationUpdate
- StockLevel (frontend-only for dashboard grouping)

**Design System:** Apple-inspired minimalist design using CSS variables (--bg, --accent, .card, .page, .section-title, nav, 
