### 3. Additional context (if relevant):
- The verify_frontend_types tool has a known limitation: it matches schemas by normalized name (e.g., BloodUnitCreate → 
blood_unit → BloodUnitResponse) and reports create DTOs as "missing" response-only fields. This is a false positive - create 
